# Ingest workflow

When user adds source to `raw/` and asks to ingest:

1. Read full source document
2. Discuss key takeaways with user before writing anything
3. Create summary page in `wiki/` named after source
4. Create or update concept pages for each major idea or entity
5. Add wiki-links (`[[page-name]]`) to connect related pages
6. Update `wiki/index.md` with new pages and one-line descriptions
7. Append entry to `wiki/log.md` with date, source name, and what changed

Single source may touch 10–15 wiki pages. Normal.
